article.description: — Tyler Rolison, Jarod Lucas and Kenan Blackshear each scored 12 points to help Nevada defeat Pacific 88-39 on Wednesday.
article.headline: Rolison scores 12 as Nevada knocks off Pacific 88-39
article.linkText: Rolison scores 12 as Nevada knocks off Pacific 88-39
article.story: RENO, Nev. -- — Tyler Rolison, Jarod Lucas and Kenan Blackshear each scored 12 points to help Nevada defeat Pacific 88-39 on Wednesday. Rolison also contributed five rebounds for the Wolf Pack (3-0). Lucas shot 4 for 13, including 2 for 7 from beyond the arc. Blackshear finished 6 of 10 from the field. The Tigers (1-2) were led by Tan Yildizoglu, who recorded eight points. Judson Martindale added seven points for Pacific. Greg Outlaw also recorded six points and three steals. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
